quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Hora (Ea Kahlolo) e se e atametse, ngoeli petsohile ka lehare"
  54,2,"Empa ha ba bona sesupo, ba ea koeneha, ba re: “Hona ke boloi ba ka mehla.”"
  54,3,"Ba nyelisa ‘nete, ba sala litakatso tsa bona morao. Empa, ntho e ngoe le e ngoe e na le nako ea pallo"
  54,4,"Ba amohetse litaba tsa temoso e feletseng, hore ba fetole metsamao ea bona"
  54,5,Bohlale bo tsotoang; empa litemoso ha li’a ka tsa thusa letho
  54,6,Kahoo ba furalle. Letsatsi leo ka lona sebohloli se tlang ho ba bitsetsa litabeng tse mahlonoko
  54,7,"Ba tla atamela, – ba soabile – mabitleng a bona, ba ts’oana le litsie ha li tletse-tletse hohle"
  54,8,Ba potlaketse ho seboholi ba tonne mahlo! – “Le thata Letsatsi.” Mahana-tumelo a tla cho
  54,9,"Batho ba habo Nooe pele ho bona ba ile ba nyefola lekhabunyane la Rona pele ho bona, ba re: “Ke lehlanya!” O ile a phalalisoa"
  54,10,"Ke moo a ileng a bitsa ho Mong`a hae: “Ke ea hlotsoeng, kahoo ak’u mpe U nthuse.”"
  54,11,Eaba Re bula mekoallo ea leholimo ka metsi a phallang
  54,12,"Le hona ho ts’akhunya liliba lefats’eng, hore metsi a tle a fihlele taelo e fanoeng"
  54,13,Eaba Re mo jara ka Areka eneng e entsoe ka lifate tsa lipalema
  54,14,"Hore e phaphamale holim’a metsi kapel’a mahlo a Rona, e le moputso ho eo ea ileng a nyelisoa"
  54,15,Re ile Ra siea seo e le sesupo; empa na ho teng ea tlang ho amohela temoso
  54,16,Empa ak’u boneng kamoo kahlolo ea ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a litemoso tsa ka
  54,17,Ka ‘nete Re entse Qura’n ho ba bobebe ho ho utloisiseha le ho hopoleha; joale na ho teng ea tla amohela temoso
  54,18,Morabe oa Ba-A’d o ile oa nyelisa. Bonang kamoo kahlolo ea Ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a litemoso
  54,19,Hobane Re ile Ra ba romella sekhobo sa phefo mohla letsatsi le nyonyehang
  54,20,Hoo e ileng ea tsokotsa batho joaloka ha eka ene ele likutu tse koqotsoeng ka metso tsa lifate tsa palema
  54,21,Bonang kamoo kahlolo ea Ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a litemoso tsa Ka
  54,22,Ruri! Re entse koran ho ba bobebe ho utloisiseha le ho hopoleha; joale na ho teng ea tlang ho amohela temoso